All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
ChartData
Internal model representing all dynamically generated chart data for a Vision Report.
ChartDataItem
Represents a single data point in a chart used within the Vision Report.
Config
Provides a fluent API for configuring global metadata of the VisionReport.
FreeMarkerEngine
Singleton engine for processing a ReportModel with FreeMarker templates to generate the final HTML report.
Log
Represents a single log entry within a test case in the Vision Report.
LogModel
Internal data model representing a single log event (step) within a test case, used by the Vision Report rendering engine.
MediaModel
Internal data model representing a fully processed media item (screenshot, visual artifact, or file preview) within the Vision Report.
MediaProvider
Represents a wrapper for media content (such as images, videos, or screenshots) used within Vision Report.
MediaProvider.MediaType
Enum representing the source type of the media.
MediaUtil
Internal utility class for converting MediaProvider sources into Base64-encoded MediaModel instances suitable for embedding in Vision Report HTML templates.
ReportGenerator
The main engine responsible for converting API objects into the internal ReportModel and generating the HTML report.
ReportModel
Represents the internal data model for an entire Vision Report.
Status
Enumeration representing the possible statuses of a test case or a log event within the Vision Report system.
SystemInfo
Represents a single piece of system information as a key-value pair.
SystemInfoModel
Internal data model representing a system information entry for the Vision Report.
Test
Represents a single test case within the Vision Report framework.
TestModel
Internal data model representing a single test case within a Vision Report.
VisionReport
The central data container for a Vision Report execution.
